## Define the function on any dataframe input x
GoPlot <- function(x) {
  
  G <-ggplot(data=RecordDF_A, aes(.data[[x]], y="") ) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", aes(fill =.data[[x]])) 
  
  return(G)
}
## Use the function in lappy
lapply(names(RecordDF_A), function(x) GoPlot(x))
